#

Lemon Ricotta Waffles

25 min
$5
320 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

DairyGluten

Dietary Tags:

Vegetarian

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Breakfast

Tags:

BreakfastBrunchSweet

Description

Fluffy waffles infused with zesty lemon and creamy ricotta, perfect for a delightful breakfast or brunch!

Ingredients

  • all-purpose flour: 1 cup
  • ricotta cheese: 1/2 cup
  • milk: 1/2 cup
  • eggs: 2
  • lemon zest: 1 tablespoon
  • baking powder: 2 teaspoons
  • sugar: 2 tablespoons
  • vanilla extract: 1 teaspoon
  • salt: 1/4 teaspoon
  • butter: for greasing the waffle iron
